I should be going now.

282
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:15,760
Please don't go, auntie. You've barely eaten anything.

283
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:17,220
I've been thinking today.

284
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:20,700
I've been causing you trouble all this time.

285
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,360
Not only have you never complained,

286
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:24,560
but you've treated me with such warmth.

287
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:27,160
To be honest, I'm already very content.

288
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:29,320
I'm tired from playing today.

289
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:31,400
Sorry, I'll head back first.

290
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:34,890
Auntie, let me walk you out.

291
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:40,640
Mrs. Qin, take care.

292
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,080
Xinxin.

293
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:53,520
Huaming is a thoughtful person.

294
00:14:54,280 --> 00:14:55,080
I can see that.

295
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:57,370
To be honest,

296
00:14:57,800 --> 00:14:59,440
with him taking care of you and the baby,

297
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,700
I feel quite relieved.

298
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:02,720
But no matter what,

299
00:15:03,160 --> 00:15:04,890
you still need a proper family.

300
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:08,370
With his financial situation,

301
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:10,400
how can he marry you?

302
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:12,530
How will he support you and your child?

303
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,320
So I still hope you

304
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:15,780
think about it carefully.

305
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,570
As I've said before,

306
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:20,520
my door is always open to you.

307
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:22,440
You can come back anytime.

308
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:25,490
Go on now.

309
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:28,040
Take care, Auntie.

310
00:15:41,040 --> 00:15:43,000
Mom, you're finally back.

311
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:45,800
Haven't I already told you

312
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:47,530
not to worry about this matter?

313
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,320
I've already made the first move,

314
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,980
but she won't give me a chance.

315
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,900
If you want to win Xinxin back,

316
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:56,740
you really need to put in some effort.

317
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:00,240
Outdo that Huaming, understand?

318
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:02,760
Mom, did I hear you right?

319
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:05,040
Why does it sound like

320
00:16:05,040 --> 00:16:06,770
you're taking Huaming's side?

321
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,640
This Huaming is just

322
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:10,080
a calculating older man.

323
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:12,930
He just plays mind games and sweet-talks,

324
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:15,120
and Wan Xinxin actually believes him.

325
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,240
Easy for you to say.

326
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:19,360
I've seen it with my own eyes.

327
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:22,660
He takes such good care of Wan Xinxin,

328
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:25,200
and he's extremely attentive.

329
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,560
His behavior

330
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:32,080
All women would appreciate

331
00:16:32,280 --> 00:16:33,680
and gladly accept.

332
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:37,360
These are clearly things you should be doing.

333
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:40,800
I just don't understand.

334
00:16:41,040 --> 00:16:42,840
How is Xinxin worse than Liu Wei?

335
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:45,380
She's kind, innocent, and sensible.

336
00:16:47,040 --> 00:16:49,770
Of course, she has her little tempers sometimes.

337
00:16:50,160 --> 00:16:52,520
But that's hardly a flaw.

338
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:56,300
The key point is she's the child's birth mother.

339
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:59,520
You need to pay attention.

340
00:16:59,880 --> 00:17:01,940
Hurry up and find a way to win her back.

341
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,160
If you wait any longer,

342
00:17:03,160 --> 00:17:05,890
she'll really become Huaming's woman, you know?

343
00:17:32,840 --> 00:17:33,370
Who is it?

344
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:48,490
Why are you here?

345
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:03,170
Look at the state you're living in.

346
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:04,920
I'm getting by.

347
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:08,880
Come on. I'm here to help you out.

348
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:11,080
No need.

349
00:18:11,080 --> 00:18:13,280
Ming already gave me a card.

350
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:17,210
That card is for paying back interest.

351
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,280
How will you manage in the meantime?

352
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:21,210
Eating instant noodles every day?

353
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:22,960
I told you I can make do.

354
00:18:23,360 --> 00:18:25,640
Make do? You can't compromise with your health.

355
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:27,640
Health is your most valuable asset.

356
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:30,840
Or as you'd say, health is essential for picking up girls.

357
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:33,810
You might die before Shi Lu even chases after you.

358
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:40,330
And no one would even know how you died.

359
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:46,800
Well...

360
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:48,840
You're giving me all your money.

361
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:49,500
It's a loan.

362
00:18:51,040 --> 00:18:53,520
If you lend me all your money, what about you?

363
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:56,520
I'll manage. Just be frugal.

364
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:59,090
What about the baby formula money?

365
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:01,770
Alright, stop being dramatic.

366
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:03,920
I still have money for baby formula.

367
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:06,960
Take this money and buy yourself some decent food.

368
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:09,290
I'm going home to check on the baby now.

369
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:09,920
Um...

370
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:12,600
Isn't Ming watching the baby?

371
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:13,160
So...

372
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:16,080
How about I treat you to a late-night snack?

373
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:17,940
I'll take you out for skewers.

374
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:21,820
Never mind.

375
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:26,210
You're really treating Hua Ming like a nanny.

376
00:19:27,120 --> 00:19:27,850
I'm leaving.

377
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:36,530
Spend it wisely.

378
00:19:39,760 --> 00:19:40,480
Thank you.

379
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:53,700
I'm so thirsty in the middle of the night and can't find water to drink.

380
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:01,290
What's with that phone call

381
00:20:01,560 --> 00:20:03,120
last night? You were talking past 3 AM.

382
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:03,800
Who was it?

383
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:07,560
Well, the situation is...

384
00:20:07,840 --> 00:20:10,120
After drinking too much last night,

385
00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:11,800
when everyone got home,

386
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:13,850
we just checked in with each other.

387
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,680
Was it Mr. Qian? CEO Qian?

388
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:18,040
Yes, CEO Qian.

389
00:20:18,080 --> 00:20:19,320
Stop lying.

390
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:20,960
I just made up a random name

391
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:22,360
and you took the bait.

392
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:24,320
Made up?

393
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:27,120
What a coincidence!

394
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:29,800
The CEO we were drinking with last night

395
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:32,660
is actually surnamed Qian. His name is Qian Duoduo.

396
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:34,800
Fine, I'll give him a call then.

397
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:36,200
No, you can't. If you make that call,

398
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:37,600
the business deal will be ruined.

399
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:38,720
It would be embarrassing.

400
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:39,840
Then you call him.

401
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,840
Xu Chunli, you can't do this.

402
00:20:46,080 --> 00:20:48,410
Don't touch my phone without permission.

403
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:49,500
Do you understand?

404
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:51,140
Let it go if you can. If not,

405
00:20:51,360 --> 00:20:53,600
hand over your bank card.

406
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:55,960
What the hell?

407
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:04,300
He always gets the upper hand.

408
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,040
I'm wrong again.

409
00:21:36,560 --> 00:21:36,960
Hello?

410
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,120
Hey honey.

411
00:21:38,760 --> 00:21:40,600
I don't have anything planned tonight.

412
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:41,800
I'll come home early.

413
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:43,680
So...

414
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:45,880
Could you make some braised pork for me?

415
00:21:46,280 --> 00:21:48,320
Add extra sugar. Make it sweet.

416
00:21:49,320 --> 00:21:49,880
What for?

417
00:21:50,240 --> 00:21:51,680
What else? To eat.

418
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:55,210
We can have some drinks together tonight.

419
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:59,280
Why are you suddenly in the mood for drinks?

420
00:21:59,280 --> 00:22:01,740
No, there's actually a reason to celebrate.

421
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:03,400
I got my bonus.

422
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:08,680
You're giving me such a big surprise.

423
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:10,340
I don't know if I can handle it.

424
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:13,210
This is just the beginning.

425
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:17,280
So there's an even bigger surprise coming?

426
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,000
Alright.

427
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:19,960
I'm busy now so I have to go.

428
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:21,320
See you tonight, okay?

429
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:33,060
Here, try this.

430
00:22:34,080 --> 00:22:36,120
This one should be to your taste.

431
00:22:41,800 --> 00:22:43,530
Did we run out of dark soy sauce?

432
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,840
I added more already.

433
00:22:45,680 --> 00:22:47,280
The color isn't dark enough.

434
00:22:47,280 --> 00:22:49,080
This braised pork needs a certain color.

435
00:22:49,080 --> 00:22:50,610
It needs to be deep and rich.

436
00:22:51,280 --> 00:22:53,140
Otherwise, it's not appetizing.

437
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:54,420
Well...

438
00:22:57,800 --> 00:23:00,000
Didn't you say you'd give me a surprise?

439
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:01,640
What surprise?

440
00:23:02,280 --> 00:23:03,480
You said so yourself.

441
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:04,400
I did?

442
00:23:06,280 --> 00:23:08,440
I said this was your surprise for me.

443
00:23:08,840 --> 00:23:11,120
You said this was just the beginning.

444
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:13,520
I asked if there was an even bigger surprise coming.

445
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:14,380
And you agreed.

446
00:23:16,480 --> 00:23:18,360
I agreed? What did I agree to?

447
00:23:19,520 --> 00:23:21,400
Let me tell you something. Life is just...

448
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:23,400
about living ordinary days.

449
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:25,200
There aren't that many surprises.

450
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:27,320
Hurry up and eat. We need to sleep after dinner.

451
00:23:27,320 --> 00:23:29,850
I have an important client meeting tomorrow.

452
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:31,920
You...

453
00:23:34,800 --> 00:23:35,660
Say that again.

454
00:23:35,760 --> 00:23:36,690
What do you mean?

455
00:23:36,720 --> 00:23:39,050
Are you having one of your episodes again?

456
00:23:39,800 --> 00:23:41,000
Just eat your dinner.

457
00:23:41,760 --> 00:23:42,560
Then tell me,

458
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:45,730
what were you doing at that clothing store today?

459
00:23:47,760 --> 00:23:48,960
What clothing store?

460
00:23:49,640 --> 00:23:51,920
Stop pretending.

461
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,840
I took pictures of you there.

462
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:57,200
Xu Chunli, you followed me?

463
00:23:58,120 --> 00:24:00,780
You followed me again. What are you trying to do?

464
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:03,920
Do you know what's most important between husband and wife?

465
00:24:03,920 --> 00:24:04,780
You don't know.

466
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:05,920
Trust.

467
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:07,610
If there's no trust,

468
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:08,720
whether we stay together or not,

469
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:10,320
I really don't care anymore.

470
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:13,560
You... you're threatening me with divorce?

471
00:24:18,040 --> 00:24:19,440
I'm not threatening you.

472
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:21,160
I'm serious.

473
00:24:31,080 --> 00:24:32,440
Hello, Lady Company.

474
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:35,840
Mr. Shi, I only have one week.

475
00:24:36,120 --> 00:24:38,120
If I can't see Wan Xinxin,

476
00:24:38,360 --> 00:24:39,290
then we're done.

477
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:41,370
You know her personality well.

478
00:24:41,520 --> 00:24:43,050
Then figure something out.

479
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:44,440
You think I really care about

480
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:45,640
that stupid car show?

481
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:47,560
What I care about is Wan Xinxin.

482
00:24:47,560 --> 00:24:48,560
I need to see her.

483
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:50,410
I need to see her regularly.

484
00:24:52,560 --> 00:24:54,160
Fine, I'll try again.

485
00:24:54,640 --> 00:24:57,040
But how the meeting goes is between you two.

486
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:59,890
I'm only responsible for getting her to meet you.

487
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:01,560
Alright.

488
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:09,440
Come in.

489
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:19,720
I actually wanted to see you too.

490
00:25:22,360 --> 00:25:24,960
Who do you think you are to speak to me like that?

491
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:26,680
What did I do?

492
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:29,240
You walked in here with an attitude.

493
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:31,080
You're doing the same thing.

494
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:32,360
You look upset too.

495
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:35,900
Go close the car show deal.

496
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:37,250
Pay back what you owe me.

497
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:40,300
No, Mr. Shi.

498
00:25:40,760 --> 00:25:41,960
Are you insisting

499
00:25:41,960 --> 00:25:43,680
that I work on this car show project?

500
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:44,040
Yes.

501
00:25:45,280 --> 00:25:46,340
If that's the case,

502
00:25:47,360 --> 00:25:48,600
then I'm really sorry.

503
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:49,760
I have no choice.

504
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:53,040
I can't sell my dignity

505
00:25:53,040 --> 00:25:54,160
for a project.

506
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:55,850
Don't you agree?

507
00:25:56,040 --> 00:25:58,120
I'll find a way to pay you back what I owe.

508
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:59,050
I'm leaving now.

509
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:10,160
I got fired.

510
00:26:12,040 --> 00:26:14,440
What else could I do? Wait for her to fire me?

511
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:17,400
What am I going to do without you?

512
00:26:18,160 --> 00:26:20,290
I won't receive yellow roses anymore.

513
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:22,420
You heartless person!

514
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:23,960
I thought you'd miss me.

515
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,880
Dream on.

516
00:26:28,520 --> 00:26:29,840
But don't worry.

517
00:26:30,560 --> 00:26:32,290
Someone's thinking about you.

518
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:39,770
Bye-bye.

519
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,340
Who sent me these flowers?

520
00:26:58,600 --> 00:26:59,260
Liu Beibei.

521
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:03,250
These yellow roses are for you.

522
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:05,560
Thank you.

523
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:09,940
No, I mean the yellow roses I gave you before.

524
00:27:21,080 --> 00:27:23,080
You don't need to bring me flowers every day.

525
00:27:23,080 --> 00:27:24,240
And stop pressuring me

526
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:25,970
to take on your boring project.

527
00:27:26,320 --> 00:27:28,360
Just so you know, I quit.

528
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:29,800
No, no, wait.

529
00:27:31,040 --> 00:27:33,440
Why did you quit? Don't be impulsive.

530
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:36,120
I wanted you to take this project

531
00:27:36,280 --> 00:27:38,320
just to help boost your performance

532
00:27:38,480 --> 00:27:39,600
and earn more money.

533
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:42,640
Of course, I also wanted to see you more often.

534
00:27:43,120 --> 00:27:44,040
Well, I'm sorry,

535
00:27:44,040 --> 00:27:45,840
but I can't fulfill your wishes.

536
00:27:46,120 --> 00:27:48,000
I don't have time to play games with you every day.

537
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,960
Seeing you now just makes me feel suffocated.

538
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:50,960
No, please don't.

539
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:52,330
Don't be angry, Xinxin.

540
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:55,080
I know some of the things I did before

541
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:57,320
were really inappropriate.

542
00:27:57,520 --> 00:27:59,050
I feel very guilty about it.

543
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,320
So I hope you can give me a chance

544
00:28:01,320 --> 00:28:02,520
to make it up to you.

545
00:28:04,680 --> 00:28:07,440
What's wrong with you? Been reading romance novels lately?

546
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:09,720
Aren't you embarrassed saying such things at your age?

547
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:10,120
Fine.

548
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:13,500
Let's get to something more practical then.

549
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:16,040
There's a car in the garage. This year's model.

550
00:28:16,040 --> 00:28:17,880
You've been taking the bus to work,

551
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:19,480
which must be quite uncomfortable.

552
00:28:19,480 --> 00:28:20,640
You should drive instead.

553
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:23,160
I've already quit. What do I need a car for?

554
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:25,980
Well, you can still use it in your daily life.

555
00:28:28,560 --> 00:28:30,490
If you had done this six months ago,

556
00:28:30,760 --> 00:28:33,120
I would have been moved to tears.

557
00:28:33,680 --> 00:28:34,480
But now,

558
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:36,400
nothing you do can make up for it.

559
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:38,130
In my heart, you're just a jerk.

560
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:42,360
Xinxin, how can you be so cold-hearted?

561
