Would he even listen to me?

838
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:32,000
You're his girlfriend.

839
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,840
If he doesn't listen to you, who will he listen to?

840
00:40:33,840 --> 00:40:35,240
We were just pretending.

841
00:40:35,240 --> 00:40:37,000
It was all for old Mrs. Qin.

842
00:40:37,800 --> 00:40:39,680
I don't care if you were pretending or not.

843
00:40:39,680 --> 00:40:41,280
You have to help me with this.

844
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:42,570
I really can't help.

845
00:40:43,960 --> 00:40:44,420
Well...

846
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:48,330
Then I won't help you with your child anymore.

847
00:40:49,120 --> 00:40:50,450
You're threatening me?

848
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:52,080
You don't care about what happens to me.

849
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:53,400
You call this a threat?

850
00:40:54,520 --> 00:40:55,760
Sis, I've noticed that

851
00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:58,490
you're being even more unreasonable than me now.

852
00:41:00,160 --> 00:41:01,220
Fine, I'm leaving.

853
00:41:01,680 --> 00:41:02,920
I won't come tomorrow.

854
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:04,600
I won't come the day after either.

855
00:41:04,600 --> 00:41:06,400
Take care of the child yourself.

856
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:09,760
Sister, how could you do this?

857
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:12,290
Please come in, auntie.

858
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:13,460
Sister,

859
00:41:14,080 --> 00:41:15,340
we're not eating here.

860
00:41:17,360 --> 00:41:18,620
Everything's ruined.

861
00:41:18,840 --> 00:41:20,700
How can I even think about eating?

862
00:41:22,200 --> 00:41:23,440
What happened, sister?

863
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,300
What's broken?

864
00:41:24,720 --> 00:41:26,380
No, the pot. The pot is broken.

865
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:30,200
Why did you two come back together?

866
00:41:30,200 --> 00:41:31,860
I ran into auntie downstairs.

867
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:35,240
How about this, auntie?

868
00:41:35,240 --> 00:41:36,320
It doesn't matter if the pot is broken.

869
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:38,580
I can make something simple for us to eat.

870
00:41:38,760 --> 00:41:39,800
No need.

871
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:42,800
If the pot is broken, I'll treat you to a meal outside.

872
00:41:42,800 --> 00:41:45,640
My sister has already left. There's no one to watch the child.

873
00:41:45,640 --> 00:41:47,640
Bring the child along to eat with us.

874
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:54,400
Grandma, order something to eat.

875
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:56,000
Did you get everything down?

876
00:41:56,200 --> 00:41:57,530
Okay, that's it for now.

877
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:06,840
Xinxin.

878
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:10,170
Are you feeling unwell?

879
00:42:10,360 --> 00:42:11,090
No, I'm fine.

880
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:13,820
I probably didn't sleep well last night.

881
00:42:15,080 --> 00:42:17,340
We've known each other for some time now.

882
00:42:17,480 --> 00:42:19,140
You can't hide things from me.

883
00:42:19,280 --> 00:42:20,810
Whatever is bothering you,

884
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:22,320
you can always talk to me about it.

885
00:42:22,320 --> 00:42:25,080
Personal or work issues, tell me everything.

886
00:42:27,200 --> 00:42:28,680
If Huaming is bullying you,

887
00:42:28,680 --> 00:42:30,140
I'll deal with him for you.

888
00:42:31,520 --> 00:42:33,200
He wouldn't dare bully me.

889
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:35,740
Right, I wouldn't dare bully her.

890
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:36,520
I don't think you would dare either.

